import PropTypes from 'prop-types'

import { ButtonBase, Link, Tooltip } from '@mui/material'

// project imports
import Avatar from '../extended/Avatar'

// ==============================|| CARD SECONDARY ACTION ||============================== //

const CardSecondaryAction = ({ title, link, icon }) => {
  return (
    <Tooltip title={title || 'Reference'} placement='left'>
      <ButtonBase disableRipple>
        {!icon && (
          <Avatar
            component={Link}
            href={link}
            target='_blank'
            alt='MUI Logo'
            size='badge'
            color='primary'
            outline
          >
            <svg
              width='500'
              height='500'
              viewBox='0 0 500 500'
              fill='none'
              xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'
            >
              <g clipPath='url(#clip0)'>
                <path
                  d='M100 260.9V131L212.5 195.95V239.25L137.5 195.95V282.55L100 260.9Z'
                  fill={'#1565c0'}
                />
                <path
                  d='M212.5 195.95L325 131V260.9L250 304.2L212.5 282.55L287.5 239.25V195.95L212.5 239.25V195.95Z'
                  fill={'#2196f3'}
                />
                <path
                  d='M212.5 282.55V325.85L287.5 369.15V325.85L212.5 282.55Z'
                  fill={'#1565c0'}
                />
                <path
                  d='M287.5 369.15L400 304.2V217.6L362.5 239.25V282.55L287.5 325.85V369.15ZM362.5 195.95V152.65L400 131V174.3L362.5 195.95Z'
                  fill={'#2196f3'}
                />
              </g>
              <defs>
                <clipPath id='clip0'>
                  <rect
                    width='300'
                    height='238.3'
                    fill='white'
                    transform='translate(100 131)'
                  />
                </clipPath>
              </defs>
            </svg>
          </Avatar>
        )}
        {icon && (
          <Avatar
            component={Link}
            href={link}
            target='_blank'
            size='badge'
            color='primary'
            outline
          >
            {icon}
          </Avatar>
        )}
      </ButtonBase>
    </Tooltip>
  )
}

CardSecondaryAction.propTypes = {
  icon: PropTypes.node,
  link: PropTypes.string,
  title: PropTypes.string,
}

export default CardSecondaryAction
